<%- include('partials/head') %>
<%- include('partials/header') %>

<section class="wrap">
  <div class="page-head">
    <h1>Privacy Policy 🔒</h1>
    <p>The short version: everything you share with us is voluntary, we guard it like our own, and we will never sell it. Ever.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="prose">
    <p><i>Last updated: 10 July 2026</i></p>

    <h2>💛 Our promise in one line</h2>
    <p>You come here to save money, not to become the product. <b>We do not sell, rent or trade your personal data to anyone.</b> Full stop, pinky promise.</p>

    <h2>📝 What you share is always your choice</h2>
    <p>Everything you give us on IndiaOffers.in is <b>completely voluntary</b>. You can browse every deal, coupon and buying guide without telling us a thing. If you choose to create an account, submit a deal, or send us a query, you decide what to share:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><b>Account details</b> — username, email, and (optionally) your mobile number, the categories you love and the bank cards you hold, so we can send you the alerts you asked for.</li>
      <li><b>Deal submissions</b> — the deal links, prices and notes you send us as a partner.</li>
      <li><b>Contact queries</b> — your name, email and message when you write to us.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>🔍 What we use it for (and nothing else)</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To run your account, credit your partner points and send the alerts you opted into.</li>
      <li>To reply to your queries at <a href="mailto:<%= support.email %>" style="color:var(--primary);font-weight:700"><%= support.email %></a> or on WhatsApp if you messaged us there.</li>
      <li>To count clicks on deals (anonymously) so we know which deals you love and can find more like them.</li>
      <li>To keep the site secure and spam-free.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>🍪 Cookies</h2>
    <p>We use a small number of cookies to keep you logged in and to remember your session — the boring, essential kind. We don't run creepy cross-site trackers.</p>

    <h2>🔗 Affiliate links (our honest living)</h2>
    <p>When you grab a deal, we send you to the store (Amazon, Flipkart and friends) through an affiliate link. If you buy, the store may pay us a small commission — <b>at zero extra cost to you</b>. That's how we keep the lights on and the loot flowing. The store handles your purchase, payment and delivery under its own privacy policy.</p>

    <h2>🛡️ How we protect your data</h2>
    <p>Passwords are stored encrypted (we couldn't read them even if we wanted to), the site runs over HTTPS, and access to user data is limited to our small team on a strict need-to-know basis.</p>

    <h2>🗑️ Your data, your rules</h2>
    <p>Want to see, change or delete anything you've shared — or close your account entirely? Just email <a href="mailto:<%= support.email %>" style="color:var(--primary);font-weight:700"><%= support.email %></a> and we'll take care of it, no questions, no hoops.</p>

    <h2>👶 Children</h2>
    <p>IndiaOffers is meant for shoppers aged 18 and above. We don't knowingly collect data from children.</p>

    <h2>🔄 Changes to this policy</h2>
    <p>If we ever change this policy, we'll update this page and the date at the top. The one thing that will never change: <b>your data is not for sale.</b></p>

    <h2>💬 Questions?</h2>
    <p>Write to <a href="mailto:<%= support.email %>" style="color:var(--primary);font-weight:700"><%= support.email %></a> or <a class="wa-link" href="<%= waUrl %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp Us</a> — a human will reply.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
